// There are some built-in commands:
Let's go! #line:03c7129 
// Wait for 2 seconds
<<wait 2>>
Hey hey! #line:036bc05 
// Wait for half a second
<<wait 0.5>>
Hey again! #line:006e386 
// Leave the dialogue now
<<stop>>

// Leave the dialogue if we don't have enough money
<<if $money < 50>>
    Shopkeeper: You can't afford my pies! #line:03bad1c 
    <<stop>>
<<endif>>
===

// You can make your own Unity C# commands and call them in similar way